<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Ab Ye Check Karo:</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Live URL open karo</strong> — Vercel ne ek <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.vercel.app</code> URL diya hoga, usse browser mein open karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Comments API test karo</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">your-url.vercel.app/api/comments</code> open karo aur check karo ke kaam kar raha hai</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Environment variables</strong> — Agar app mein database use ho rahi hai, to <strong>Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables</strong> mein apni <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.env</code> file ki values add karo, warna API calls fail hongi</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
