<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Tumhari website deploy ho gayi hai aur admin panel bhi kaam kar raha hai. Bas ye 2 links yaad rakho:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Tumhare Important Links:</h2>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Page</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">🌐 <strong>Main Website</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://amazcart.vercel.app</code></td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">🔐 <strong>Admin Panel</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://amazcart.vercel.app/admin</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Kaise Use Karna Hai:</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Customer</strong> website dekhe ga → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Tum (Admin)</strong> products, orders, comments manage karo → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app/admin</code></li>
</ol>
