ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Achha sawaal hai! Abhi tumhara admin panel <strong>bilkul secure nahi hai</strong> — dekho kyu:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">❌ Abhi Kya Masla Hai:</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Password hardcoded hai</strong> — code mein likha hua hai, koi bhi GitHub pe dekh sakta hai</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Token simple hai</strong> — easily guess ho sakta hai</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Koi rate limiting nahi</strong> — koi bhi unlimited baar password try kar sakta hai</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>HTTPS pe hai</strong> — ye acha hai ✅</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">✅ Secure Banane Ke Liye Karo Ye:</h2>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">1. Password Environment Variable Mein Rakho</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Kabhi bhi password code mein mat likho! Vercel pe jao:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables</strong></p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Code" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
  items-center
  justify-center
