<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">📊 <strong>Dashboard</strong> — stats (products, comments count)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">📦 <strong>Products</strong> — add, edit, delete, search</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">💬 <strong>Comments</strong> — dekhna aur delete karna</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">🖼️ <strong>Image Upload</strong> — product image upload</li>
</ul>
