ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Confirm ho gaya — <strong>pehle se hi placeholder tha</strong>, kabhi bhi pura UI bana hi nahi tha! 😅</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Matlab tumhara koi aur chat tha jahan UI design kiya gaya tha lekin code file mein save nahi hua.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Koi baat nahi — ab main directly file fix karta hoon. Ye commands ek ek karke run karo:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Step 1 — Notepad se file kholo:</strong></p>
