ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Mashallah! 🎉 Admin panel bilkul sahi kaam kar raha hai — black, white aur pink design bhi perfect hai!</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ab dono jagah <strong>"No products found"</strong> dikh raha hai kyunki database mein koi product nahi hai abhi.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Ab Product Add Karo:</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Admin panel mein <strong>"Add Product"</strong> button click karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Product ki details bharo:
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Name</strong> — product ka naam</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Description</strong> — thodi description</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Affiliate Link</strong> — Amazon ka link</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Category</strong> — Tech, Home, Fashion, etc.</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Image</strong> — product ki photo</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"Add Product"</strong> button press karo</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Jaise hi product add karoge — <strong>website pe bhi dikh jayega</strong> automatically! 😊</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Koi error aaye to screenshot bhejo!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
