ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Dekh liya! Tumhara original design tha — ab samajh gaya! 😊</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Original admin panel mein tha:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>White background</strong> with orange <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem] inline-flex items-center h-5"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 border-[0.5px] border-border-200 rounded flex-shrink-0 shadow-sm mr-1 align-middle" style="background-color: rgb(255, 107, 53);"></span>#FF6B35</code> colors</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Stats cards</strong> upar</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Add product + Products list</strong> side by side ek hi page pe</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Simple clean design</strong> — koi black sidebar nahi tha!</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Notepad se file kholo:</p>
