<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app/admin</code></strong> kholo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"Add new product"</strong> form mein jao</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"Upload product image"</strong> field mein <strong>image file select karo</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"Add product"</strong> button dabao</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Lekin pehle batao — image upload karne ke baad kya error aata hai ya image save nahi hoti?</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ye command run karo aur output paste karo:</p>
