ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ohh! Product card mein jo <strong>khali grey box</strong> dikh raha hai — wahan product ki image nahi hai!</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ye isliye hai kyunki <strong>database mein products ka <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">image_url</code> empty hai.</strong></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">Fix — Admin se Product Add Karte Waqt Image Zaroor Upload Karo:</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app/admin</code> jao</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Add new product</strong> mein product ka naam, description, link sab bharo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>"Upload product image"</strong> mein koi bhi product ki photo select karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Add product</strong> dabao</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Lekin pehle ye batao:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Kya tumne pehle se koi product add kiya hua hai bina image ke?</strong> Agar haan to:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Admin panel mein us product ke <strong>Edit</strong> button dabao</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Image upload karo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Update</strong> karo</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Phir website pe refresh karo — image dikh jayegi! 😊</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
