ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Based on our conversation, here's your project description:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">AmazCart — Project Description</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>AmazCart</strong> is an affiliate product store website built with <strong>Next.js (App Router)</strong>. It is deployed on <strong>Vercel</strong> and connected to a <strong>GitHub</strong> repository for automatic deployments.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">What it does:</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">AmazCart is a curated Amazon affiliate product listing website where users can browse, search, and discover top Amazon products across different categories. Every product link redirects to Amazon via an affiliate link.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Features:</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>User Side:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Browse products by category — Tech, Home, Fashion, Books, Sports, Beauty</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Search products</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">View product details and comments</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Clean orange/white/beige design</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Admin Side:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Secure password-protected admin panel at <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/admin</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add, edit, delete products</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Upload product images</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">View comments</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Dashboard with stats (total products, comments, clicks)</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Tech Stack:</h3>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Framework</strong> — Next.js (App Router)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Hosting</strong> — Vercel</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Auth</strong> — JWT token based admin login</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Storage</strong> — Environment variables for secrets</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Version Control</strong> — GitHub</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Links:</h3>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Website</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Admin Panel</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">amazcart.vercel.app/admin</code></li>
</ul>
