ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Here's a description you can give to any AI image generator (like ChatGPT, Midjourney, Canva AI, etc.):</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Prompt:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Design a modern, minimalist logo for an e-commerce website called "AmazCart". The logo should be a square icon of 512x512 pixels. Use a shopping cart icon combined with the letter "A" or a spark/star symbol. Color scheme: bold orange (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem] inline-flex items-center h-5"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 border-[0.5px] border-border-200 rounded flex-shrink-0 shadow-sm mr-1 align-middle" style="background-color: rgb(255, 107, 53);"></span>#FF6B35</code>) as the main color on a clean white background with dark black (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem] inline-flex items-center h-5"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 border-[0.5px] border-border-200 rounded flex-shrink-0 shadow-sm mr-1 align-middle" style="background-color: rgb(26, 26, 26);"></span>#1A1A1A</code>) accents. The style should be flat design, professional, and suitable for a tech-savvy online shopping brand. No text, just the icon mark. Sharp edges, clean lines, suitable for use as a favicon.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Ye prompt <strong>Canva, ChatGPT, Adobe Firefly, DALL-E</strong> mein paste karo — acha logo mil jayega! 😊</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Logo ban jaye to batao — main bataunga kaise website pe lagana hai!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
